cast.overview: Decades since their successful television series was canceled, Chip has succumbed to a life of suburban domesticity as an insurance salesman. Dale, meanwhile, has had CGI surgery and works the nostalgia convention circuit, desperate to relive his glory days. When a former cast mate mysteriously disappears, Chip and Dale must repair their broken friendship and take on their Rescue Rangers detective personas once again to save their friend’s life.
cast.title: Chip 'n Dale: Rescue Rangers

details.biography: Victor Turpin is a Colombian actor and singer who pursued his dream in the artistic field. He is known for various movies named Shades of Blue (2018), Ma (2019), Will & Grace (2018), and Murder Mystery. In addition to these movies, he also landed marvelous roles in movies like Killing Hasselhoff and Greenlight. A talented artist Victor also had a wonderful career in the music industry as he worked with many talented producers and songwriters including Kevin DeClue. Moreover, in 2009, he also released the music album TODO with original songs written himself
details.name: Victor Turpin
